      <title>矿业交易商 Froneman 退休，Sibanye 任命 Stewart 为首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/mining-dealmaker-neal-froneman-retires-as-sibanye-names-stewart-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资深交易员尼尔·弗罗内曼 (Neal Froneman) 将卸任 Sibanye Stillwater Ltd. 首席执行官一职，并于九月底将这家南非矿业公司的管理权移交给理查德·斯图尔特 (Richard Stewart)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/mining-dealmaker-neal-froneman-retires-as-sibanye-names-stewart-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 14:05:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普监管有助于银行整合：鲍勃·戴蒙德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/trump-regulation-to-aid-bank-consolidation-bob-diamond-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Atlas Merchant Capital 创始合伙人兼首席执行官 Bob Diamond 认为，美国银行整合“非常具有建设性”，将在未来三年内将金融机构数量减少到“1,000 至 2,000 家之间”，并分析了特朗普政府下预期的监管环境。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/trump-regulation-to-aid-bank-consolidation-bob-diamond-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 14:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩因南非十年禁令展开法律斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/bain-locked-in-legal-battle-over-decade-long-south-african-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝恩公司因卷入腐败丑闻而正在与南非金融和税务当局展开法律斗争，试图推翻长达十年的与该国开展业务的禁令。]]></description>
